				<td colspan="2"><span>I just finished this portion and camped the listed spawn point for a total of 23 hours (in about 6 hour segments).
<br />

<br />
Spawn interval is 13 minutes and Eldrig WILL eventually pop.  There aren't too many mobs in that general area and  you should be able to fear kite him there.   You will be right on top of him when he pops, so pulling isn't really an issue.
<br />

<br />
It would be easier if you could find a cleric looking for shards and team up in between spawns.  This way you can probably melee Eldrig without too much trouble.
<br />

<br />
Good luck.
<br />

<br />
Mehlodian - 65 Bard - Erollisi Marr</span></td>
